to each serve a total sentence in prison
of four years and three months.

673
01:21:39,228 --> 01:21:41,521
Hanna Schmitz,

674
01:21:41,605 --> 01:21:45,316
in view of your own admissions
and your special role,

675
01:21:45,401 --> 01:21:48,403
