721
01:27:39,004 --> 01:27:42,757
"Straightaway, she began
to swear the oath that I required.

722
01:27:42,841 --> 01:27:44,926
Never, she would never do me harm.

723
01:27:45,010 --> 01:27:47,428
And when she'd finished then, at last,

